Arch Linux PKGBUILD, mainly for improved width handling of (wide) glyphs via
wcwidth(3) callback.

WIP at https://github.com/blueyed/rxvt-unicode/pull/1.
README: https://github.com/blueyed/rxvt-unicode/blob/wcwidth-hack/README.md

Packaging for Arch Linux (this PKGBUILD) has moved to
https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/rxvt-unicode-wcwidthcallback.
